# Database and Prisma

This project uses Prisma ORM with a PostgreSQL database.

## Key Files
- [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) - Database schema definition

## Models
- `Post` - A basic model with id, name, and timestamps

## Commands
- `pnpm db:generate` - Generate Prisma client after schema changes
- `pnpm db:push` - Push schema changes to the database
- `pnpm db:studio` - Open Prisma Studio for database visualization
- `pnpm db:migrate` - Apply migrations to the database

## Database Setup
Run `./start-database.sh` to initialize a PostgreSQL database locally.